      "widgets_values": [
        "A highly detailed, adorable 3D cartoon render of a fluffy white bunny, posed inquisitively amidst a vibrant fantasy forest. The bunny is outfitted in miniature explorer gear, featuring a moss-green vest, tiny khaki shorts, and a small leather satchel strapped across its chest. The forest is otherworldly, dominated by fantastical, oversized mushroom-like trees with brightly colored caps and textured, bark-like stalks. Soft, dappled sunlight filters through the canopy, casting a magical, whimsical glow on the scene. The color palette is rich with deep emerald greens, earthy browns, and pops of bioluminescent color from the flora. Shot with a low-angle wide-shot to emphasize the scale of the mushrooms, utilizing a Pixar-esque rendering style with smooth textures and high saturation, achieving photorealistic quality within the stylized cartoon aesthetic."
